| 54 | `IpcClient.hpp` | `poll()` held `m_cbMutex` while calling callbacks — deadlock on any IPC action | Moved mutex unlock before callback invocation |
| 55 | `IpcClient.hpp` | Unquoted exe path in `CreateProcessA` — spaces in folder name caused silent failure | Wrapped path in double quotes |
| 56 | `gui-nuklear/src/main.cpp` | No startup timeout — loading spinner never cleared on backend failure | Added 5-second timeout; shows error message |
| 57 | `IpcClient.hpp` | Python escaping mangled quotes in `CreateProcessA` cmd string | Fixed escape handling |
| 58 | `IpcClient.hpp` | Windows `ReadFile` buffer 4096 bytes — BCD responses larger, partial reads, no callbacks | Increased to 65536 bytes; added accumulation loop |
| 59 | `IpcClient.hpp` | `ipcParseEntries` used `find('}')` — BCD GUIDs contain `}`, truncating every entry | Replaced with newline-delimited field parsing |

